den=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col bg-slate-50\"><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white border-b border-slate-200 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between h-16\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0\"><a class=\"text-xl font-bold text-red-650 tracking-wider hover:opacity-90\" href=\"/\">DIGICAKRA</a></div><nav class=\"hidden md:flex space-x-8\"><a class=\"relative text-sm font-semibold transition-colors py-2 px-1 text-red-600 font-semibold border-b-2 border-red-600\" href=\"/#layanan\">Layanan</a><a class=\"relative text-sm font-semibold transition-colors py-2 px-1 text-slate-600 hover:text-red-600\" href=\"/#cara-kerja\">Cara Kerja</a><a class=\"relative text-sm font-semibold transition-colors py-2 px-1 text-slate-600 hover:text-red-600\" href=\"/#promo\">Promo</a><a class=\"relative text-sm font-semibold transition-colors py-2 px-1 text-slate-600 hover:text-red-600\" href=\"/tracking\">Tracking Pesanan</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-white bg-red-600 rounded hover:bg-red-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500 focus:ring-offset-2 transition-all shadow-sm\" href=\"/order\">Pesan Sekarang</a><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center p-2 rounded text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-100 focus:outline-none md:hidden transition-all\" aria-controls=\"mobile-menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Toggle Main Menu</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5.5 w-5.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></header><section id=\"layanan\" class=\"relative overflow-hidden text-white py-24 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(\n              rgba(0,0,0,0.6),\n              rgba(0,0,0,0.6)\n            ),\n            url(&#x27;/assets/img/gmbar.webp&#x27;)\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10 pb-8\"><span class=\"hero-anim-item opacity-0 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white/20 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-red-400 ring-1 ring-inset ring-red-500/20 mb-4 animate-pulse\">Inovasi Digital Pembayaran BRIDA 2026</span><h1 class=\"hero-anim-item opacity-0 text-4xl sm:text-5xl sm:p-2 font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6\">Solusi Satu Pintu Fotokopi &amp; ATK Cakrawala</h1><p class=\"hero-anim-item opacity-0 text-lg sm:px-4 sm:text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Upload file Anda dari rumah, bayar dengan QRIS secara instan, lacak status secara real-time, dan ambil pesanan Anda saat sudah siap!</p><div class=\"hero-anim-item opacity-0 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4\"><a class=\"w-xs md:w-auto inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-red-600 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-red-900/30\" href=\"/order\">Cetak Dokumen Online</a><a href=\"#katalog\" class=\"w-xs md:w-auto inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-md hover:bg-slate-700 transition-all shadow-md\">Belanja ATK Toko</a></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-28 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-50 to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div></section><section id=\"cara-kerja\" class=\"py-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900\">Cara Kerja DIGICAKRA</h2><p class=\"text-slate-600 mt-2\">Pemesanan dokumen Anda menjadi sangat mudah dengan 4 langkah praktis</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div class=\"step-anim-card opacity-0 bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm relative group hover:border-red-300 transition-all\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-red-100 group-hover:text-red-200 transition-all block mb-4\">01</span><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2\">Konfigurasi &amp; Upload</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Isi nama &amp; WA, unggah file PDF/DOCX/Gambar, dan pilih spesifikasi warna/jilid.</p></div><div class=\"step-anim-card opacity-0 bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm relative group hover:border-red-300 transition-all\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-red-100 group-hover:text-red-200 transition-all block mb-4\">02</span><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2\">Bayar QRIS Instan</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Scan kode QRIS dinamis di layar HP Anda menggunakan aplikasi bank/e-wallet pilihan.</p></div><div class=\"step-anim-card opacity-0 bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm relative group hover:border-red-300 transition-all\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-red-100 group-hover:text-red-200 transition-all block mb-4\">03</span><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2\">Kami Proses Segera</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Staf kami langsung memproses dokumen/pesanan Anda sesuai antrean.</p></div><div class=\"step-anim-card opacity-0 bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm relative group hover:border-red-300 transition-all\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-red-100 group-hover:text-red-200 transition-all block mb-4\">04</span><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2\">Lacak &amp; Ambil</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Pantau status pesanan lewat nomor WhatsApp. Ambil di toko tanpa perlu mengantre.</p></div></div></section><section id=\"promo\" class=\"py-8 bg-red-50 border-y border-red-100\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-gift w-8 h-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M20 11v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8\"></path><path d=\"M7.5 7a1 1 0 0 1 0-5A4.8 8 0 0 1 12 7a4.8 8 0 0 1 4.5-5 1 1 0 0 1 0 5\"></path><rect x=\"3\" y=\"7\" width=\"18\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-red-950\">Program Loyalitas Stempel Digital!</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-red-800\">Kumpulkan stempel digital dengan memesan produk lewat WhatsApp. Dapatkan reward potongan harga menarik setiap kelipatan 10 stempel!</p></div></div><a class=\"w-full md:w-auto inline-flex justify-center items-center px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-red-700 bg-red-100 rounded-md hover:bg-red-200 transition-all border border-red-200\" href=\"/tracking\">Cek Stempel Saya</a></div></section><section id=\"katalog\" class=\"py-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex-grow\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900\">Katalog Alat Tulis Kantor</h2><p class=\"text-slate-600 mt-2\">Daftar perlengkapan ATK berkualitas yang tersedia langsung di toko kami</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full border transition-all bg-slate-900 border-slate-900 text-white\">Semua</button></div><div class=\"relative\"><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Cari ATK...\" class=\"w-full md:w-64 px-4 py-2 text-sm bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:border-red-600 transition-all\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"flex sm:flex-col md:flex-row gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden animate-pulse w-full h-full\"><div><div class=\"aspect-video w-full bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"p-6 space-y-4\"><div class=\"h-3 bg-slate-200 rounded w-1/4\"></div><div class=\"h-5 bg-slate-200 rounded w-3/4\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"h-3 bg-slate-200 rounded w-full\"></div><div class=\"h-3 bg-slate-200 rounded w-5/6\"></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-2\"><div class=\"h-5 bg-slate-200 rounded w-1/3\"></div><div class=\"h-3 bg-slate-200 rounded w-1/6\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"px-6 pb-6 pt-0 border-t border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 flex items-center justify-center h-16\"><div class=\"h-9 bg-slate-200 rounded-md w-full\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden animate-pulse w-full h-full\"><div><div class=\"aspect-video w-full bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"p-6 space-y-4\"><div class=\"h-3 bg-slate-200 rounded w-1/4\"></div><div class=\"h-5 bg-slate-200 rounded w-3/4\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"h-3 bg-slate-200 rounded w-full\"></div><div class=\"h-3 bg-slate-200 rounded w-5/6\"></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-2\"><div class=\"h-5 bg-slate-200 rounded w-1/3\"></div><div class=\"h-3 bg-slate-200 rounded w-1/6\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"px-6 pb-6 pt-0 border-t border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 flex items-center justify-center h-16\"><div class=\"h-9 bg-slate-200 rounded-md w-full\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden animate-pulse w-full h-full\"><div><div class=\"aspect-video w-full bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"p-6 space-y-4\"><div class=\"h-3 bg-sl